# --- keep the build lean, but do NOT exclude Backend/ ---

# Git & editor junk
.git
.gitignore
**/.git
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/.DS_Store

# Node caches
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
**/package-lock.json.orig

# Build outputs you don't want in context
**/dist
**/.next
**/.cache
**/coverage
**/tmp

# IMPORTANT: explicitly keep the app code
!Backend/**
